#./deploy generated/sea dev-2:/var/www/vhosts/vocabs.digitalcommons.coop/www/essglobal/V2a
#./deploy generated/sea prod-2:/var/www/vhosts/vocabs.digitalcommons.coop/www/essglobal/V2a

